WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.306 --> 00:00:09.009
For parents always, always

2
00:00:10.243 --> 00:00:12.112
believe your child.

3
00:00:12.112 --> 00:00:15.382
I don't care how popular the coach is,
I don't care

4
00:00:15.815 --> 00:00:18.151
how what a winning season

5
00:00:18.518 --> 00:00:21.588
the coaches had or anything.

6
00:00:21.588 --> 00:00:26.493
If your child comes to you
and says that something has happened,

7
00:00:27.360 --> 00:00:31.731
something has happened.
And you need to speak

8
00:00:31.731 --> 00:00:35.602
with the authorities about it
because something has definitely happened.

9
00:00:36.069 --> 00:00:40.340
And if you don't believe your child,
what will happen is that child

10
00:00:40.340 --> 00:00:46.079
will shut down and never talk
about these types of tough subjects again.

11
00:00:46.713 --> 00:00:48.882
And that's the worst thing you can do

12
00:00:49.249 --> 00:00:52.352
because that opens
the door for more violations.

